The author is the founder of Simpol, the [[International Simultaneous Policy Organisation]]

=Endorsement=

Scilla Elworthy, founder of the Oxford Research Group and a long-time campaigner for nuclear disarmament, gave the following endorsement for John’s new book on global governance and Simpol, Global Domestic Politics – A Citizen’s Guide to Running a Diverse Planet, published earlier this year:

“I think it’s a terrific book. You are writing with great clarity and it makes all the difference that you bring in Spiral Dynamics and Integral thinking. This allows you to make such strong points about diverse values and non-democratic nations. Until I read your clear analysis, I hadn’t realised just how much destructive international competition is central to governments’ problems”.


